Underwriter Moseley Holding Corp&lt;MOSE> said an initial public offering of 500,000 common sharesof Candlewood Bank and Trust Co is underway at 10 dlrs pershare.    It said it has been granted an option to buy up to 75,000more shares to cover overallotments.  Directors and officers ofthe bank are expected to buy about 110,000 common shares at thepublic offering price, it said. Reuter&#3;